gure></span><span style="color: #696969;"><figure class="post__image post__image--wide"><img loading="lazy"  src="https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/Mini-Badger-go-kart.jpg" alt="" width="1339" height="994" sizes="100vw" srcset="https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Mini-Badger-go-kart-xs.jpg 300w ,https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Mini-Badger-go-kart-sm.jpg 480w ,https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Mini-Badger-go-kart-md.jpg 768w ,https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Mini-Badger-go-kart-lg.jpg 1024w ,https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Mini-Badger-go-kart-xl.jpg 1360w ,https://lztlab.github.io/media/posts/2/responsive/Mini-Badger-go-kart-2xl.jpg 1600w"></figure></span><span class="texteditor-inline-fontsize" style="color: #696969;">/</span><span class="texteditor-inline-fontsize" style="color: #696969;"> </span><span class="texteditor-inline-fontsize" style="color: #696969;">Records from the product testing phase.<br></span>
